flowRoot.flowPara: Place foam marshmallows tightly spaced on the light gray wavy lines to form a road. Use Ozoblockly to get the Evo to the End while obeying traffic rules.
+ Draw a color card and a traffic rule card => do the traffic rule whenever Evo sees the color underneath (ex: Red + Stop, Blue + Construction Zone, Green + Stop and Blink Lights)
+ Repeat until all Color Cards are assigned a rule
+ Use the sensors to know which way to turn
+ When Evo sees Black color underneath, end the program and play the "Disco" lights and say the color at the finish.
Extra Credit: Add barriers inside the roadway
Extra Credit: Draw new traffic rules and update
